266
00:17:05.969 --> 00:17:08.239
Aku tidak pernah melihat Bu Myung semabuk ini.

267
00:17:11.009 --> 00:17:12.779
Sampai jumpa, Joon Young.

268
00:17:12.910 --> 00:17:14.380
Maksudku, Sekretaris Yoon.

269
00:17:19.650 --> 00:17:20.759
Permisi.

270
00:17:22.019 --> 00:17:24.229
Kamu di sini sebagai pegawai Grup JK,

271
00:17:24.690 --> 00:17:26.430
