272
00:17:28.959 --> 00:17:30.200
Jangan khawatir.

273
00:17:40.140 --> 00:17:44.979
Hari kepindahan Eun Tae Hee. Bangun.

274
00:17:45.479 --> 00:17:46.749
Aku tahu.

275
00:17:51.150 --> 00:17:53.049
Masa bodoh. Dia bisa sendiri.

