00:26:08.719 --> 00:26:09.779
Apa?

374
00:26:10.789 --> 00:26:12.289
Tidak ada riwayat kecelakaan?

375
00:26:12.650 --> 00:26:13.719
Tidak ada.

376
00:26:13.989 --> 00:26:15.019
Kenapa?

377
00:26:15.789 --> 00:26:16.890
Tunggu.

378
00:26:18.289 --> 00:26:21.059
